edu.illinois.cs.cogcomp.nlp.utilities

Class HeadFinderBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.illinois.cs.cogcomp.nlp.utilities.HeadFinderBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollinsHeadFinder

    public abstract class HeadFinderBase
extends Object
    This is mainly an abstract class for the Collins' head finder. It allows for head information to be found in other ways, though.

    This file is based on the similar file from the Stanford NLP code, rewritten to talk nicely to the other parts of this package.

    Author:
    Vivek Srikumar
